The BusinessTech Online FinTech Conference 2022 is now live, and you can watch all it has to offer online and on-demand. Click here to watch the BusinessTech Online FinTech Conference 2022 The BusinessTech Online FinTech Conference is an event for banking, ICT, and FinTech executives and professionals. The conference will cover a variety of topics – including FinTech disruption, mobile payments, digital banking, cryptocurrency, and blockchain – and is possible thanks to its excellent sponsors. Nedbank has joined the conference as an Event Partner. BCX has joined the event as a Platinum Sponsor, and our Gold Sponsors include VALR and Altron Arrow. Many companies have also joined the conference as interview partners. BusinessTech has secured great speakers for the online conference. The Online FinTech Conference will be hosted by respected business personality Michael Avery. Avery will then interview the country’s top FinTech players. This includes: Nedbank Executive of Emerging Innovation – Chipo Mushwana
